Clerics who take the Pride domain seek to improve their self image, and are granted spells that reflect their ambitious nature.

<b>Domain Special Ability and Bonus Spells</b>
- Epic Resilience: The character no longer automatically fails saving throws on a roll of 1. The character will still fail the save if their result fails to equal or beat the DC.

- The cleric gains access to the following spells at the specified spell level: <i>Heroism (3), Greater Heroism (7), Mass Charm Monster (9)</i>.